’Ů@3134d6d5173373549c48b84e10dd9f1764abe125245d6747d584c58076080257ŮęTitle: title: plugin rm
Path: Flags
Content:
``--plugin-config {path}``
: Use a plugin registry file other than the one set in 
``$nu.plugin-path``
.
``--force, -f``
: Don't cause an error if the plugin name wasn't found in the file.
